title: Photos: Shahid Kapoor & Mira Kapoor Party With The ‘Rangoon’ Team
text:
Rashmi Daryanani Jan . 7 . 2017 
The Rangoon trailer released yesterday to positive reviews, and it looks like the team got together for a small celebration afterwards. Saif Ali Khan and Kangana Ranaut were missing, but Shahid Kapoor was there along with Mira and director Vishal Bhardwaj . 
Have a look at the photos co-producer Warda Nadiadwala posted: 
— Warda S Nadiadwala (@WardaNadiadwala) January 7, 2017 And some more love right back at u'l from team #Rangoon ???? #SaifAliKhan #KanganaRanaut u were missed pic.twitter.com/oph11Y5yih 
— Warda S Nadiadwala (@WardaNadiadwala) January 7, 2017 
The film is due for release on February 24th. Catch the trailer here in case you missed it! 0
